  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate, in an intensive care unit, the reproducibility between
      two non-cardiologists operators and a cardiologist expert in echocardiogram, of the Simpson
      method and of the calculation of GLS for the evaluation of the systolic function of the left
      ventricle in critically ill patients intubated and ventilated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
